  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA337-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">1. itu tōḻi talaimakaṉ poruḷvayiṉ pirital uṟṟāṉatu kuṟippaṟintu viḷakkiyatu.
            2. tōḻi ulakiyal kūṟi pirivuṇarttiyatūumām.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">1. This is who the confidante explained after having understood the intention of HIM who was set on separating. 2. It is also how the confidante informed about the separation, talking about the nature of the world.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA337">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            ulakam paṭaitta kālait talaiva</l>
<l>            maṟantaṉar kollō ciṟantici ṉōrē</l>
<l>            mutirā vēṉi letiriya vatiral</l>
<l>            parāraip pātirik kuṟumayir māmalar</l>
<l>            naṟumō rōṭamō ṭuṭaṉeṟin taṭaicciya</l>
<l>            ceppiṭan taṉṉa nāṟṟan tokkuṭa</l>
<l>            ṉaṇiniṟaṅ koṇṭa maṇimaru ḷaimpāṟ</l>
<l>            ṟaḷarnaṟuṅ katuppiṟ paiyeṉa muḻaṅku</l>
<l>            marumpeṟaṟ perumpayaṅ koḷḷātu</l>
<l>            pirintuṟai marapiṉ poruḷpaṭait tōrē</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O the foremost one of the time the world was created,</l>
<l>has he forgotten, he who was excellent,</l>
<l>– he who created wealth</l>
<l rend="indent4">[along] with the custom of remaining separate,</l>
<l rend="indent">	without taking in the big yield difficult to obtain,</l>
<l rend="indent2">when it gently thunders:<note place="foot">What is conveyed by <term xml:lang="ta">muḻaṅkum</term> here? Is the message that the rainy season is about to start, but that the god does not pay heed to it by sending HIM home?</note> of slackening fragrant hair</l>
<l rend="indent2">in five parts, resembling sapphire taken as an adorning colour,</l>
<l rend="indent2">gathering together the fragrance as if a vessel was upturned</l>
<l rend="indent3">in which were enclosed, all thrown together, with the fragrant</l>
<l rend="indent3">Mōrōṭam</l>
<l rend="indent3">the furry dark flowers of the large-trunked trumpet flower tree</l>
<l rend="indent3">[and] wild jasmine facing the summer not yet there?</l>
      </lg>
      </div>
